This is a script simplying pat's building process.

==============
    Usage
--------------
1. Copy `build.sh`
copy this script out of ${PAT_SRC}. For example, if you download pat source code
at /opt/pat, then you should copy this script in /opt

 [user@localhost]$ cp ./build.sh ../../../ && cd ../../../

2. Run `build.sh`
You can build `pat` at three different levels: debug, optimized and normal.
The default level is normal.

Usage:
  ./build.sh [pat source] [dbg|opt|normal]

Example:
  [user@localhost]$ ./build.sh ./pat dbg

or
  [user@localhost]$ ./build.sh ./pat
